    "question_id" : 12102777,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Also is possible to assign different action implementing onCancelListener:</p>\n\n<pre><code>alertDialog.setOnCancelListener(new DialogInterface.OnCancelListener(){                   \n    @Override\n    public void onCancel(DialogInterface dialogInterface) {\n        //Your custom logic\n    } \n});\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3743853,
      "reputation" : 423,
      "user_id" : 3113018,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/64bcfd3afe17adc39aab897b3c542ad3?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "BillOverFlow",
