    "body" : "<p>Alert Dialog is deprecated so use Dialog dialog = new Dialog(this);</p>\n\n<p>For prevent close on outside touch</p>\n\n<pre><code>dialog.setCanceledOnTouchOutside(false);\n</code></pre>\n"
