    "question_id" : 12102777,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In jetpack compose, use <code>dismissOnClickOutside = false</code> property to prevent from closing.</p>\n<pre><code>    AlertDialog(\n        title = {\n            Text(&quot;Title&quot;)\n        },\n        text = {\n            Text(text = name)\n        },\n        onDismissRequest = onDismiss,\n        confirmButton = {\n            TextButton(onClick = onDismiss ) {\n                Text(&quot;Yes&quot;)\n            }\n        },\n        dismissButton = {\n            TextButton(onClick = onDismiss ) {\n                Text(&quot;Cancel&quot;)\n            }\n        },\n        properties = DialogProperties(\n            dismissOnClickOutside = false\n        )\n    )\n</code></pre>\n<p>}</p>\n"
  } ],
